OL,4,CMexico sues US gun manufacturers over
OL,5,Carms trafficking
OL,6, The Mexican government has sued some of
OL,7, the biggest US gun manufacturers,
OL,8, accusing them of fuelling bloodshed
OL,9, through reckless business practices.
OL,11,FThe lawsuit alleges that the companies
OL,12,Fknew they were contributing to illegal
OL,13,Farms trafficking, which has been linked
OL,14,Fto many deaths.
OL,16,FOfficials say Mexico is seeking as much
OL,17,Fas $10bn (#7.2bn) in compensation,
OL,18,Fthough any amount would be decided by
OL,19,Fthe court.
OL,21,FThe companies have not yet commented.
